text: Eugène Anselme Sébastien Léon Desmarest (1816–1889) was a French zoologist and entomologist. He was the son of Anselme Gaëtan Desmarest (1734–1838). ==Works== Partial list: * In: Jean-Charles Chenu, . Marescq et Compagnie, Paris. v.18, p. 123– 181 (1860). * . In: J–C.
